      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 764,
      "width": 415,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "A boat has a speed of 10 km/h in still water and the\nstream flows at 3 km/h. Find the upstream and downstream\nspeeds of the boat.",
      "fontSize": 13,
