    {
      "id": "el_45",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1229,
      "width": 238,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Down=20/2=10, Up=20/4=5\n  B+S=10, B-S=5 → subtract: 2S=5\nStep 2: S=2.5 km/h\n\nTRICK (formula):\nS = (Down-Up)/2 = (10-5)/2 = 2.5\nB = (Down+Up)/2 = (10+5)/2 = 7.5\n\n  ~~~ DOWN ~~~     ~~~ UP ~~~\n  20km / 2hrs      20km / 4hrs\n  =10 km/h         =5 km/h\n\nAnswer: Stream speed = 2.5 km/h ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 4500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 45,
      "isDeleted": false,
