      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Down=20/2=10, Up=20/4=5\n  B+S=10, B-S=5 → subtract: 2S=5\nStep 2: S=2.5 km/h\n\nTRICK (formula):\nS = (Down-Up)/2 = (10-5)/2 = 2.5\nB = (Down+Up)/2 = (10+5)/2 = 7.5\n\n  ~~~ DOWN ~~~     ~~~ UP ~~~\n  20km / 2hrs      20km / 4hrs\n  =10 km/h         =5 km/h\n\nAnswer: Stream speed = 2.5 km/h ✓",
