    },
    {
      "id": "el_50",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1629,
      "width": 267,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Down=16, Up=8. Let D=distance\n  Total=2D, Time=D/16+D/8=3D/16\nStep 2: Avg=2D/(3D/16)=32/3=10.67\n\nTRICK (Harmonic Mean):\nAvg = 2×Down×Up/(Down+Up)\n= 2×16×8/24 = 256/24 = 10.67\nALT: (B²-S²)/B = (144-16)/12 = 10.67\n\n  START ══════ D ══════ PLACE\n    GO:   B+S=16 ──→  T1=D/16\n    BACK: B-S=8  ←──  T2=D/8\n\nNOTE: Avg < B always! (stream slows)\n\nAnswer: Avg speed = 10.67 km/h ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 5000,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 50,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_7"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Down=16, Up=8. Let D=distance\n  Total=2D, Time=D/16+D/8=3D/16\nStep 2: Avg=2D/(3D/16)=32/3=10.67\n\nTRICK (Harmonic Mean):\nAvg = 2×Down×Up/(Down+Up)\n= 2×16×8/24 = 256/24 = 10.67\nALT: (B²-S²)/B = (144-16)/12 = 10.67\n\n  START ══════ D ══════ PLACE\n    GO:   B+S=16 ──→  T1=D/16\n    BACK: B-S=8  ←──  T2=D/8\n\nNOTE: Avg < B always! (stream slows)\n\nAnswer: Avg speed = 10.67 km/h ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
