      "x": 535,
      "y": 1548,
      "width": 415,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "A man can row 6 km upstream in the same time as he rows 10\nkm downstream. If the speed of the stream is 2 km/h, find\nthe speed of the man in still water.",
      "fontSize": 13,
