      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1975,
      "width": 415,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "A swimmer covers 30 km downstream in 3 hours and 18 km\nupstream in 3 hours. Find the speed of the swimmer in\nstill water and the speed of the stream.",
